<div>
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome</h1>
    <h3>Sample App - Wrapper Basics</h3>
    <p>
        The MinistryPlatform API Wrapper simplifies the development process for .NET software developers.  This Nuget package
        allows rapid development against the API and provides a sound starting point for development.  This web application
        provides several standard samples to assist in getting started.
